Package: TweetScraperR
Type: Package
Title: Scrape Posts and User Data from X Twitter
Version: 0.4.0
Description:
    Provides functions to extract data from X/Twitter, including posts
    (tweets), users, and associated metadata, without using the official
    APIs. It allows collecting data from X/Twitter and handling the
    responses conveniently in R, with a focus on easing data collection
    for analysis and visualization. Este paquete proporciona funciones
    para extraer datos de X/Twitter (publicaciones, usuarixs y metadatos
    asociados) y facilita la recolección de datos para análisis y
    visualización.
URL: https://github.com/agusnieto77/TweetScraperR
